{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8103","title":"NG8103: Missing control flow directive","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8103-missing-control-flow-directive\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"enerauatyzuky521qtfevi42h\">NG8103: Missing control flow directive<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8103#ng8103-missing-control-flow-directive\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8103#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"erccmlatefqdqp7m1vx3pjh7s\">此诊断确保在模板中使用已知控制流指令的独立组件 （例如\n<code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a></code>、\n<code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code>、\n<code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a></code>）时，还应导入这些指令，要么逐个导入，要么通过导入\n<code><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a></code>。或者，使用 Angular 的内置控制流。</p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  standalone: true,\n  // Template uses `*<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>`, but no corresponding directive imported.\n  template: `&lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"visible\"&gt;Hi&lt;/div&gt;`,\n  // …\n})\nclass MyComponent {}\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-fix-the-problem\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4104vumb4tnmcc2gj7acor39r\">如何解决此问题<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8103#how-to-fix-the-problem\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b6g98but5rra7ebg19hqm9aad\">使用 Angular 的内置控制流。</p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  standalone: true,\n  template: `@if (visible) { &lt;div&gt;Hi&lt;/div&gt; }`,\n  // …\n})\nclass MyComponent {}\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9fjwza9gu8km3wkidegpek9dk\">或者确保导入相应的控制流指令。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9hx8zgcy6lg329n8d3pbm9j8h\">指令可以单独导入：</p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\nimport {<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgIf</a>} from '@angular/common';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  standalone: true,\n  imports: [<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgIf</a>],\n  template: `&lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"visible\"&gt;Hi&lt;/div&gt;`,\n  // …\n})\nclass MyComponent {}\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c01k3wiocz5amjihf6ss96r3e\">或者导入整个 <code><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a></code>，其中包含所有控制流指令：</p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\nimport {<a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a>} from '@angular/common';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  standalone: true,\n  imports: [<a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a>],\n  template: `&lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"visible\"&gt;Hi&lt;/div&gt;`,\n  // …\n})\nclass MyComponent {}\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/NgFor\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/common/NgSwitch\n - api/core/Component\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103#how-to-fix-the-problem\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103#ng8103-missing-control-flow-directive\n-->"}